{"tid":596172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好佩服誠哥做生意嘅眼光？","createTime":"2018-03-17T11:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T15:00:46.000Z","uid":86587,"like":44,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c66af08a87abc74b114dcdd2d02a33a56e0420","tid":596172,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"6, 70年代工業起飛，佢靠穿膠花起家<br />\n到80年代，知道地產發展係香港將來，轉行做地產<br />\n後來蛇吞象收購埋和黃做綜合發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來大陸發生64事件，好多發展商卻步，佢係第一步打入中國市場飲頭啖湯嘅人<br />\n到習總啱啱上任佢一早知有唔妥就撒資，雖然受到好強嘅官媒壓力，但時間證明佢決定正確，睇吓遲咗走佬嘅王健林下場幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最佩服就係做到咁大都緊貼最新科技，入股Facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢嗰兩個仔就無咁好眼光，捉到鹿唔識脫角，入股騰訊好快就賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n縱觀咁多年，基本上無一個重要嘅生意決定係錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個小學程度嘅人吊打哂啲咩哈佛MBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做生意嘅眼光真係神嘅等級，唔怪得阿Richard咁崇拜佢老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841c039165d3d007f3f2ca733f88c367a48a8a6d","tid":596172,"uid":73,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"有邊個唔佩服?"},{"pid":"6adbef6001cbeac340fd38e5ed5d6a3f92c59ac8","tid":596172,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:15:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f4789049b48ca6d0f85f4b55e67eeb11e7664cf","tid":596172,"uid":171107,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"我佩服佢識搵有錢老婆多啲"},{"pid":"a9e094c4f72ec66371d267ea2246ee232f07f2ae","tid":596172,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bdbf59c5a3192f7067fba0bf88a318e2621c8a","tid":596172,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"佩服佢搵到有米老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ef8190099fa0ca13539b3a5b0ff33203b3af18","tid":596172,"uid":165187,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:35:41.000Z","msg":"佢係一早就明白：you can't choose your father, but can choose your father in law. 呢句話的真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6389223977b11545305417197814376ac8069bc4","tid":596172,"uid":170157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"其實佢打造佢既王國果陣，佢老婆幫左好多手，甚至有時一d 好有前瞻性既決定都係佢老婆既主意，比誠哥更加獨具慧眼，只係後來佢老婆係佢事業最輝煌果陣退左落黎，專注家庭，慢慢傳媒係報導果陣就忽略左佢老婆既功勞"},{"pid":"bd1ce6e22609e495dbc002500945c3c1f89b8cca","tid":596172,"uid":86587,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:40:48.000Z","msg":"樓上成班葡萄撚，唔肯承認同學習人地成功嘅地方，一味話人靠老婆，咁嘅心態真係抵你地成世做廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fc995331aff73ec9aa31e3dac4c301170dffe5","tid":596172,"uid":174074,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"你打既所有野我係tvb李家誠回顧特輯到睇過晒<br />\n會唔會抄得太足？"},{"pid":"a0e1da8bcf1c73cf6bfb23323de663bb64876a7e","tid":596172,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我剩係知家陣在香港 白手要做佢今時今日咁 機會都近乎0"},{"pid":"5745b1a8fc6d7b79423328272f60662dd97cb6b7","tid":596172,"uid":86587,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5fc995331aff73ec9aa31e3dac4c301170dffe5","tid":596172,"uid":174074,"like":4,